    <note>Bi(1) Zhongyan [1416] He used his grandfather's yin to enter the civil service. Author of the Zhongshu beidui (ordered in 1078). Zhongyou's [1417] brother, Shian's [8107] great grandson. Shian's fifth generation descendant was Liangshi [1418]. Zhongyan served on an ad hoc committee in 1080. His father Conggu's [3709] first wife was Mei(1) Xun's [1361] daughter and his second wife was Chen(1) Yaosou's [97] granddaughter. XCB, 287.16b-17a, 298.1b, 7a, 299.13b, 307.5b, 308.1a, 325.12b. Bi Zhongyou, WJ, 16.24b-30b. CBD, 3, 2713.</note>
